eventinfo: MindMajix’s Apache Kafka training enables us to develop real-time streaming data pipelines and applications that follow the data streams. It also empowers you to integrate storage, stream processing, and messaging to analyze real-time and historical data. This Apache Kafka course includes the concepts like Zookeeper, Producer, consumer, replication, High-level Kafka architecture, and Partition. Along with training sessions, we also provide real-time projects and industry scenarios to get a practical understanding of Single broker installation, Console Consumer, Retention time, Zookeeper configuration, Kafka server, and Offset Explorer. Join our Apache Kafka online training to become a certified Apache Kafka Developer.

eventinfo: This ArcSight Training course teaches you all the essentials of the ArcSight solution, as well as provides information on how to design a complete solution. First, the course covers the basic operations of ArcSight, such as ArcSight download, install, deploy, troubleshoot, and more. Next, you’ll get a brief overview of ArcSight architecture, how to use the Console and Command Center to monitor security events, manage users, configure SIEM ArcSight, and ESM network intelligence resources. This online ArcSight Training also introduces you to searching and running reports with ArcSight Logger. Finally, you’ll gain the necessary hands-on expertise to clear ArcSight Certification through interactive labs and detailed use-cases.

eventinfo: MindMajix Quality Assurance (QA) Training helps participants to understand the core concepts of Software Testing and Information Technology that help them excel as a Quality Assurance (QA) Specialist. Our Online QA Course also covers physical products in pre-production, determining defects in manufactured products and preventing them, Sandbox Environment Vs Production Environment, SDLC-Software Development Life Cycle, Mantis Bug Tracker, and more. Additionally, during this QA online training, you’ll learn how to decipher the application of static and dynamic techniques, perform boundary value analysis, conduct walk-throughs and audits, organize test development processes as well as create a quality analysis and test plan hands-on through this QA certification course.

eventinfo: This SSAS training focuses on designing BI solutions that need implementing multidimensional data models, tabular data models and maintaining OLAP cubes. By the time when you’re done with this SSAS certification course, you’ll know how to build a tabular BI semantic model.

eventinfo: Mindmajix Qlik Sense online training provides you with in-depth expertise on the Qlik Sense tool. Our Qlik Sense virtual classroom training allows the trainees to master business intelligence and Qlik Sense features, Qlik Sense advantages, Qlik Sense navigation, data warehouse concepts and Qlik Sense installation. During this instructor-led training, you will get hands-on knowledge of Qlik Sense desktop, App overview, Qlik Sense filters and group by clause, data model viewer and load editor through two real-time projects.  Through this course, you will achieve an in-depth understanding of Qlik Sense joins, sheet properties, Charts, MTD & YTD concepts, and Set analysis. By the end of this Qlik Sense training, you will be able to clear the Qliksense Business Analyst Certification and start your career as a Certified Data Visualisation Professional.

eventinfo: The TIBCO ActiveSpaces training by MindMajix combines the performance and features of messaging software, caching systems, and database performance to support highly volatile sets of data and event-driven applications. The training course offers a basic understanding of distributed in-memory data grid that is capable of increasing the processing speed; hence, reducing expenses on transactional systems. Furthermore, the course also simplifies the concepts of Distributed System of Record, Querying, ACID-compliant NoSQL Data Grid, Zero cost for development, and entry-level production. The Lab Sessions includes the TIBCO ActiveSpaces Use Cases while working with real-time projects.

eventname: Leverage the Growing Demand for Certified Gerrit Professionals
eventinfo: One of the most common sayings is team-work can simply overcome all of the key challenges associated with a task. This is the reason why most of the businesses encourage team work. Actually, it assures a secure and an error free work environment all the time. Another benefit is the results of many minds are always better than one. When it comes to computer coding, this approach always derives numerous benefits for business. The Gerrit approach is one of the perfect examples of this. It is basically a team code collaboration tool that is purely based on the web. Coders make use of it to check out modification on the source code by different developing teams. It is closely associated with GIT. Presently, even some of the well-known organizations such as Oracle and Microsoft have considered Gerrit technology to avoid errors and assures top-class results. You can simply get the Gerrit training and can change your life by working with some of the best Information Technology companies after getting your certification.
